Class AbstractScene

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Scene
scenes.AbstractScene
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.event.EventTarget
Direct Known Subclasses:
AppointmentScene, CustomerScene, Home
public abstract class AbstractScene extends javafx.scene.Scene
Abstract class that most scenes will have. This class instantiates several services and helps to reduce code redundancy
